content:
Run Tests for Data Cloud-Triggered Flows

Create and manage specific scenarios to test your Data Cloud-triggered flows. With tests, you can quickly verify that your flow is behaving as intended without having to manually configure debug parameters for each debug run.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic in all editions.

How: In Flow Builder, click View Tests to create and manage tests.
title: Run Automated Tests for Data Cloud-Triggered Flows in Salesforce
